title: Shokhrukh Kirgizboev
text:
Shokhrukh Kirgizboevich Kirgizboev (born 3 August 1987) is a <a href="Tajikistan">Tajik</a> professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player who currently plays for <a href="FC%20Istiklol">FC Istiklol</a>.
Career.
Club.
On 7 August 2021, <a href="FC%20Istiklol">Istiklol</a> announced the signing of Kirgizboev.
International.
Kirgizboev made his senior team debut on 13 December 2018 against <a href="Oman%20national%20football%20team">Oman</a>, which ended as their 1–2 loss.
